apdu

public int apdu(byte[] RequestData,
                FedmIscTagHandler_Result result)
         throws java.lang.Exception,
                FePortDriverException,
                FeReaderDriverException,
                FedmException
APDU transfer

Parameters:
result - FedmIscTagHandler_Result object containing return values
Returns:
operation status

Description:
[0xB2][0xBE] T=CL - APDU command

The return value status indicates the success:
0 - tramsmission was successful
status byte (>1), if the reader signals a problem
error code (<0), if something goes wrong
The result object of type FedmIscTagHandler_Result contains only valid APDU data (in data member), if the operation status is 0.
Throws:
java.lang.Exception
FedmException
FePortDriverException
FeReaderDriverException
